      • onUpdate

        void onUpdate(org.ogn.commons.beacon.AircraftBeacon beacon,
            org.ogn.commons.beacon.AircraftDescriptor descriptor,
            String rawBeacon)
        Parameters:
        beacon - aircraft beacon
        descriptor - static aircraft descriptor. If an aircraft is not recognized by the system the isKnown() descriptor's method will return false. It is up to the implementing class to verify if descriptor is "known", as in case of unknown descriptor its attributes are lilely to be null.
        rawBeacon - raw beacon as received from the remote system
